<P>A SERMON Preached before the HONORABLE HOUSE of REPRESENTATIVES, On the Day intended for the Choice of COUNSELLORS, Agreeable to the ADVICE of the CONTINENTAL CONGRESS.</P>
<P>By WILLIAM GORDON, Pa&s;tor of the Third Church in ROXBURY.</P>
<P><HI>WATERTOWN:</HI> Printed and Sold by BENJAMIN EDES.</P>
<P>M<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="3 letters">LXXV</P>
</DIV1>
