<PB REF="014073_0003_0F92DB758F585070">
<OPENER><DATELINE>In the Hou&s;e of REPRESENTATIVES, <DATE>July 19, 1775.</DATE></DATELINE></OPENER>
<P><HI>ORDERED,</HI>
That Mr. <HI>Wheeler,</HI> Dr. <HI>Church,</HI> Mr. <HI>Hopkins,</HI> Col. <HI>Otis,</HI> and Col. <HI>Palmer,</HI> be a Com|mittee to return the Thanks of the Hou&s;e to the Rev. Mr. GORDON, for the Sermon deliver'd by him in the Fore|noon, and to de&s;ire a Copy of it for the Pre&s;s.</P>
<CLOSER>Atte&s;t. <SIGNED><HI>Samuel Freeman,</HI> Clerk.</SIGNED></CLOSER>
